name: Tiny Device #06: Trend-o-Meter
description: This #OBJKT shows up-to-date search trends for 'NFT'. You can explore the graph data by: 1) Rotating the knob, 2) Mouse wheel, 3) Keyboard Left & Right arrows. Switch between different time scales with: 1) Buttons, 2) '1-5' or 'HDWMY' keyboard keys. Made by https://twitter.com/neelts.
